Python3 Kafka Implementation for microbenchmarks

pip3 install kafka-python --user

Utilities:
./gen_kafka_topics.sh  = To generate kafka topics required for the experiment
./del_kafka_topics.sh  = To delete kafka topics created during the experiment
./list_kafka_topics.sh = To list kafka topics present in the system

(Note: Set KAFKA_HOME in the above scripts to home directory of kafka)

Each ot the other .sh script is the orchestrator for the micro-benchmarks.

$> mkdir data
$> ./micro-sequence-2fn.sh

This will generate a file sequence-2fns.out in data directory


